wikipedia_page.main: John Stanley James "Johnny" Williams (16 August 1935 – 24 November 2011) was an English footballer who played as a wing half. He played in the Football League for Plymouth Argyle and Bristol Rovers, amassing 481 appearances over a 14-year period.
